== Examples ==
====Just icon====
<code><nowiki>{{credits}}</nowiki></code>

{{credits}} 
====Bigger icon====
<code><nowiki>{{credits|size=64}}</nowiki></code>

{{credits|size=32}} 
====With value====
<code><nowiki>{{credits|420}}</nowiki></code>

{{credits|420}} 
